  <div id="text-content_cab5cdc9-65fb-4083-b5bd-5630035cb9fb" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Select the file you want to upload and click <strong>Open </strong>to begin uploading the file. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="monitor_file_upload_1" data-step-uuid="1db42e0b-1e26-47b8-856f-3b2736203a35">
